---
title: Chorizo, Chicken & Pumpkin Risotto with Parmesan Cheese
description: This rich pumpkin risotto comes together in the oven, leaving you to kick your feet up and enjoy quality time with the ones who matter. With the luxurious addition of chorizo and chicken, it takes this delicious and fragrant meal to the next level – taste it and see!
